---
import Icon from './Icons.astro';
---

<section class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Why Healthcare Facilities Choose MedGuard</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        We're not just another generator company. We're healthcare compliance experts.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="bg-blue-100 w-20 h-20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <Icon name="hospital" size={36} class="text-[#0F2D35]" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">100% Healthcare Focus</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">We only service medical facilities. We know AHCA, Joint Commission, and CMS requirements inside out.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="bg-green-100 w-20 h-20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <Icon name="smartphone" size={36} class="text-[#0F2D35]" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Digital Compliance Portal</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">24/7 access to all maintenance records. Never scramble for paperwork during inspections again.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="bg-orange-100 w-20 h-20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <Icon name="lightning" size={36} class="text-[#F25C2A]" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">4-Hour Emergency Response</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">When generators fail, lives are at risk. We guarantee rapid response when you need us most.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="bg-purple-100 w-20 h-20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <Icon name="users" size={36} class="text-[#0F2D35]" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Bilingual Service Teams</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">English and Spanish certified technicians ensure clear communication with your entire staff.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

